<p style="text-align: center">From this page, you can create new weddings, go to existing weddings to edit their recipes, delete weddings, and add weddings to the cart.</p>
<h1 class="title">ALL WEDDINGS</h1>

<div class="text-center" id="create-wedding-button-container">
  <a id="create-wedding-button" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseNew" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
    Create New Wedding
  </a>
</div>

<div class="collapse text-center" id="collapseNew">
  <div class="well">
    <%= render "new" %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row wedding-row">
    <% @weddings.each do |wedding| %>
      <%= render "wedding_card", wedding: wedding, order_item: @order_item %>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-8">
    <%= button_to "Update All", weddings_update_all_weddings_path, class: "btn btn-secondary", id: "update-button" %><p>This button cycles through the flower database and updates the flower prices of all the weddings. Any flowers that don't have a match (because they were deleted from the database), turn red and their price is set to zero.</p>
  </div>
</div>
